{"tid":1650603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"畢業前最大尺度衝擊！「歐吉桑殺手」23歲AKB48 阿部瑪利亞遮不住水滴奶","createTime":"2019-10-13T04:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T10:46:01.000Z","uid":9573,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"475750ab1e9ddfb4068da0abaefc7e5f08c11416","tid":1650603,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-10-13/900/20191013001048.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-10-13%2F900%2F20191013001048.jpg&h=bfe3f540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿部瑪利亞日前宣布將從AKB48 Team TP畢業。<br />\n<br />\n23歲日本女偶像阿部瑪利亞加入AKB48近10年，2年前轉戰到台北姊妹組合AKB48 Team TP發展，外型甜美和綜藝感十足，讓她擁有超高人氣，下個月將滿24歲的她，日前拋出震撼彈，決定從團體畢業，19日台北演唱會將是她以成員身分最後一次現身，近日她也替雜誌拍攝寫真，大尺度上空入鏡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/08/26/2896904_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F08%2F26%2F2896904_1.jpg&h=534c4034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下個月將滿24歲的阿部瑪利亞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-10-13/900/20191013001049.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-10-13%2F900%2F20191013001049.jpg&h=7349f5de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿部瑪利亞上空捧乳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-02-08/900/20180208004724.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-02-08%2F900%2F20180208004724.jpg&h=213d2e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與瑪利亞有同姓之親的阿部寬。<br />\n<br />\n阿部瑪利亞在日本就有「歐吉桑殺手」封號，從AKB48移籍到AKB48 Team TP依舊擁有高人氣，不過她因為「年齡」決定退團，認為自己現在不適合在新的團體中發展。其隊友、克羅地亞中場靈魂莫迪歷今季亦於銀河艦隊亦諸事不順，並預告會續留台灣演藝圈工作，而近日她也替雜誌拍攝最後寫真，上空用手遮2點，水滴奶和深溝遮不住，性感又火辣十足。"},{"pid":"a6c3d4121d60a41114efe52260db82436488298d","tid":1650603,"uid":152123,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-10-13/900/20191013001049.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n個樣好似啪咗藥之後除衫咁"},{"pid":"991a498c5d3c6eaf2336eff5b88379e8758e995a","tid":1650603,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:01:27.000Z","msg":"其隊友、克羅地亞中場靈魂莫迪歷今季亦於銀河艦隊亦諸事不順"},{"pid":"0e94e4db91b04e2afd0b1accf5154a0e22394e1d","tid":1650603,"uid":3212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"拍a片"},{"pid":"f73f83da8374c6d990c9f55b61b9aa794e31d6e0","tid":1650603,"uid":34561,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:04:40.000Z","msg":"與瑪利亞有同姓之親的阿部寬。<br />\n<br />\n其隊友、克羅地亞中場靈魂莫迪歷今季亦於銀河艦隊亦諸事不順，並預告會續留台灣演藝圈工作"},{"pid":"1d493cc58db341af2473825adf67016dae1302a0","tid":1650603,"uid":11254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:04:56.000Z","msg":"千雪呢"},{"pid":"656b1f0b70ce691b322d2ee4c0a3ac88e1ea7b5c","tid":1650603,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:06:09.000Z","msg":"塊面咁撚長"},{"pid":"187cbca01d164cd4c638ec493608f047de9e5d2b","tid":1650603,"uid":119688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"我對波都大過佢"},{"pid":"3983493b1c83dbb139744e17582bec22177b9686","tid":1650603,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:09:32.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過10